TI  - Thirty years of connectivity conservation planning: an assessment of factors influencing plan implementation
AU  - Keeley, Annika T H
AU  - Beier, Paul
AU  - Creech, Tyler
AU  - Jones, Kristal
AU  - Jongman, Rob HG
AU  - Stonecipher, Grace
AU  - Tabor, Gary M
